des: Today's top country hits, along with all-time favorites from the 90s and 2K, in long 20 in a row Wolf runs make 96.5 the Wolf the home of Starved Rock's best country! Rise & Grind weekdays with Jaimie & Chris, then let the Wolf keep you company with the most country throughout your workday. On the weekend cut loose with Bdub Radio Saturday night, Kix Brooks & Bobby Bones counting down the week's biggest hits and more of Starved Rock's best country in long 20 in a row Wolf runs!
